data.title: SUU Releases Dean's List for Fall 2023
data.meta_description: Each semester, students at Southern Utah University who attain academic excellence are named to the Dean's List.
data.text:
Published: January 10, 2024 | Author: Southern Utah University | Read Time: 9 minutes

Each semester, students at Southern Utah University who attain academic excellence are named to the Dean's List. For undergraduate students, criteria include enrollment in at least 15 credit hours during the fall semester and at least a 3.60 grade point average (on a 4.00 scale).

Congratulations to the following student for being named to the Fall 2023 Dean's List.
